{"tid":2018371,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實讀歷史嗰啲大學生，碩士，教授不如出句聲","createTime":"2020-05-15T14:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T20:00:47.000Z","uid":304634,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9a4d716f15358ddf395d9ad99782fd0ea4bd83b0","tid":2018371,"uid":304634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"有嗰博士生都寫咗篇文<br />\n你地覺得有問題不如都寫篇文出嚟反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有教DSE 歷史嗰班人ar  <br />\n你地班學生就嚟俾班官僚主義嘅人玩死<br />\n<br />\n今日都有中學校長出聲<br />\n趁機出聲la <br />\n去接受蒙面interview 又好<br />\n點都好<br />\n<br />\n班藍絲已經開始干擾香港學術自由<br />\n喺未來一定又會將中史變成必修科<br />\n<br />\n遲D 歷史科內容可能要經過中共審查完先可以教<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fea48e1aa30ef33f2009c66635b9b0b17c8eb5c","tid":2018371,"uid":228143,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:48:26.000Z","msg":"咪得蕭生敢出聲<br />\n<br />\n蕭生真爺爺"},{"pid":"df963afe4e32df4eeee5b27a19d70589764a9177","tid":2018371,"uid":294562,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"啱！我理解根本係好平常嘅問題，無人叫佢一定要同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fd797a385a494f362db41d54539a997a8e5b72","tid":2018371,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df963afe4e32df4eeee5b27a19d70589764a9177","tid":2018371,"uid":294562,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"啱！我理解根本係好平常嘅問題，無人叫佢一定要同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:54:49.000Z","msg":"蕭生直頭笑考評局垃圾喎"},{"pid":"d5095c1bdb017d4dfe66b2fe5f1b03ae9ec6d474","tid":2018371,"