科內容可能要經過中共審查完先可以教<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"知日部屋fb (中大日研系主任吳偉明）<br />\n<br />\n記得以前在新加坡國立大學教書的時候， 有一次出的試題是:「 你認為釣魚台主權應屬於哪一方？」 大部分同學都說中國， 也有說台灣， 衹有一個說日本。 我給主張主權歸於日本的同學高分， 這是因為他的論說比較有邏輯，跟我個人的看法完全沒有關係。 這便是自由思考。 如果將教育當作政治宣傳， 以後禁止所有open-ended問題好了！"},{"pid":"b19aebe5e5f2fbc038a55f322544f516b4f5e71a","tid":2018371,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18fd797a385a494f362db41d54539a997a8e5b72","tid":2018371,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df963afe4e32df4eeee5b27a19d70589764a9177","tid":2018371,"uid":294562,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"啱！我理解根本係好平常嘅問題，無人叫佢一定要同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:54:49.000Z","msg":"蕭生直頭笑考評局垃圾喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:25:23.000Z","msg":"燒山一開波講咗重點, 要吸引人讀, 所以出卷出到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩野應該直接放老毛段感謝落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca6317cd3e8f383f3c82992f27edcee04916bf1","tid":2018371,"uid":123151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T16:36:10.000Z","msg":"真係要多啲有資格嘅人出聲<br />\n喺fb睇到啲藍絲cm就知佢哋真係冇讀過書<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話咩題目有引導<br />\n而家咪就係出題考你識唔識囉<br />\n而家係考試呀唔係而家先學㗎"},{"pid":"7192c525a41139221645072424477327d91e6608","tid":2018371,"uid":167289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b19aebe5e5f2fbc